HEADWORD: Maqui
<hw>Ma"qui</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <fld>(Bot.)</fld> <def>A
Chilian shrub (<spn>Aristotelia Maqui</spn>). Its bark furnishes strings
for musical instruments, and a medicinal wine is made from its
berries.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

